## Compose vs XML

### XML
```xml
<TextView
    android:id="@+id/text"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
    android:text="Hello" />
```

```kotlin
val text = findViewById<TextView>(R.id.text)
text.text = "Hello, World!"
```

### Compose
```kotlin
@Composable
fun Greeting(name: String) {
    Text("Hello, $name!")
}
```

短、快、type-safe。

## 基本元件

```kotlin
@Composable
fun MyScreen() {
    Column(
        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize().padding(16.dp),
        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.Center,
        horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally
    ) {
        Text("Hello", style = MaterialTheme.typography.headlineLarge)
        Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(16.dp))
        Button(onClick = { /* ... */ }) {
            Text("Click me")
        }
    }
}
```

## State

### remember
```kotlin
@Composable
fun Counter() {
    var count by remember { mutableStateOf(0) }

    Column {
        Text("Count: $count")
        Button(onClick = { count++ }) {
            Text("+")
        }
    }
}
```

### Lift state up
```kotlin
@Composable
fun MyScreen() {
    var count by remember { mutableStateOf(0) }

    Counter(count = count, onIncrement = { count++ })
    Display(count = count)
}

@Composable
fun Counter(count: Int, onIncrement: () -> Unit) { ... }
```

## ViewModel + Compose

```kotlin
class CounterViewModel : ViewModel() {
    private val _count = MutableStateFlow(0)
    val count: StateFlow<Int> = _count

    fun increment() { _count.value++ }
}

@Composable
fun CounterScreen(viewModel: CounterViewModel = viewModel()) {
    val count by viewModel.count.collectAsState()

    Button(onClick = viewModel::increment) {
        Text("Count: $count")
    }
}
```

## Navigation

```kotlin
val navController = rememberNavController()

NavHost(navController, startDestination = "home") {
    composable("home") { HomeScreen(navController) }
    composable("detail/{id}") { backStackEntry ->
        val id = backStackEntry.arguments?.getString("id")
        DetailScreen(id = id, navController = navController)
    }
}

// 跳轉
navController.navigate("detail/123")
```

## Theme

```kotlin
@Composable
fun MyAppTheme(content: @Composable () -> Unit) {
    MaterialTheme(
        colorScheme = lightColorScheme(
            primary = Color(0xFF6200EE),
            secondary = Color(0xFF03DAC6)
        ),
        typography = Typography(...),
        content = content
    )
}
```

## 心法
- Compose 是新 default
- 宣告式 = state 變、UI 變
- ViewModel + StateFlow + collectAsState 黃金組合
- Material Design 3 預設
- Preview 看 UI 不用跑 emulator

**☕ 用人話講**

Jetpack Compose 完整心法——**Android UI 的新範式、取代 XML**。**一句話記住**：像從手寫排版進化到「所見即所得」——Compose 是 Android UI 的新標準，寫起來爽很多、改起來也快。

## Dart 進階

### Null safety
```dart
String name = "Alice";       // 不能為 null
String? maybeName;            // 可以為 null

// Null check
if (maybeName != null) {
    print(maybeName.length);   // 自動 narrow type
}

// 安全 access
print(maybeName?.length);     // null 時不 crash
```

### Late
```dart
late String name;  // 用前必 init

name = "Alice";    // OK
print(name);
```

### Spread + cascade
```dart
final list = [1, 2, ...other, 3];

final user = User()
  ..name = "Alice"
  ..age = 25;
```

### Records (Dart 3+)
```dart
(String, int) parseName(String s) {
    return (s.toUpperCase(), s.length);
}

final (name, len) = parseName("alice");
```

### Pattern matching (Dart 3+)
```dart
switch (user) {
    case User(name: 'Alice'):
        print('Hi Alice');
    case User(name: String n) when n.startsWith('B'):
        print('B user');
    default:
        print('Other');
}
```

## Flutter 心法

### Widget 樹
```dart
class MyApp extends StatelessWidget {
    @override
    Widget build(BuildContext context) {
        return MaterialApp(
            home: Scaffold(
                appBar: AppBar(title: Text("Home")),
                body: Center(child: Text("Hello!")),
            ),
        );
    }
}
```

### State management

#### Provider（簡單）
```dart
class CounterModel extends ChangeNotifier {
    int _count = 0;
    int get count => _count;

    void increment() {
        _count++;
        notifyListeners();
    }
}

// 用
ChangeNotifierProvider(
